<LegalPage
  pageTitle="Privacy Policy — Parody Mechanical Solutions LLC"
  pageDesc="How we handle the personal information you share through this site: what we collect, why, how long we keep it, and your choices."
  title="Privacy Policy"
  updated="July 19, 2026"
>
  <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Parody Mechanical Solutions LLC</strong> is a limited liability
    company based in Tooele, Utah, USA. Contact:
    <a href="mailto:kevinparody135@gmail.com">kevinparody135@gmail.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
  <p>We only process information you provide to us voluntarily:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Contact form:</strong> name, company (optional), email, phone,
      city, service type, a description of your request and, if you include
      them, details about your equipment or fleet.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Direct communications:</strong> whatever you include when you
      email or call us.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Our use of cookies and similar technologies is described in the
    <a href="/cookie-policy">cookie policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>3. How we use it</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to your request and prepare a quote.</li>
    <li>To schedule and deliver the service you hire us for.</li>
    <li>To meet legal, accounting, or tax obligations.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We do not use your information to send unsolicited advertising, and we do
    not sell or share your personal information as those terms are defined
    under US state privacy laws (such as the CCPA).
  </p>

  <h2>4. Who we share it with</h2>
  <p>
    We do not disclose your information to third parties except for service
    providers we need to operate (for example, email or web hosting
    providers), and authorities when the law requires it. Our providers only
    process data on our instructions.
  </p>

  <h2>5. How long we keep it</h2>
  <p>
    We keep the information related to your request for as long as our
    business relationship lasts and, afterwards, for the time needed to
    handle potential legal obligations. Requests that don't lead to a service
    are deleted within a reasonable period.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Your choices and rights</h2>
  <p>
    You may ask us at any time to access, correct, or delete your
    information, or to stop processing it, by emailing
    <a href="mailto:kevinparody135@gmail.com">kevinparody135@gmail.com</a>.
    Depending on your state of residence, you may have additional rights
    under state privacy laws; we honor such requests regardless of where in
    the US you live. We will respond as soon as possible and within any
    legally required timeframe.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Security</h2>
  <p>
    We apply reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your
    information against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Children</h2>
  <p>
    This site is intended for businesses and adults. We do not knowingly
    collect personal information from children under 13.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    If we modify this policy, we will publish the updated version on this
    page with the revision date at the top.
  </p>
</LegalPage>
